376
00:29:47.495 --> 00:29:49.413
[Candies rustling]

377
00:29:49.997 --> 00:29:51.123
Gimme those back!

378
00:29:52.458 --> 00:29:53.667
[Screams]

379
00:29:53.751 --> 00:29:55.211
Let me go! Please!

380
00:29:55.294 --> 00:29:56.128
Let me go!

381
00:29:56.253 --> 00:29:57.880
Get off of me! Help me!

382
00:29:57.963 --> 00:29:58.839
Help me!

383
00:29:58.923 --> 00:30:01.383
[♪♪♪]

384
00:30:20.903 --> 00:30:21.737
Let me go!

385
00:30:21.821 --> 00:30:23.572
Get off of me! Help me!

386
00:30:23.656 --> 00:30:24.865
Help me!

387
00:30:27.535 --> 00:30:28.661
[Thuds]

388
00:30:28.786 --> 00:30:30.955
[♪♪♪]

389
00:30:45.928 --> 00:30:47.972
- Trick or treat!
- Trick or treat!

390
00:30:49.098 --> 00:30:50.349
You guys look great!

391
00:30:50.474 --> 00:30:52.893
- Thank you Miss Jocelyn.
- Thank you Miss Jocelyn.

392
00:30:52.977 --> 00:30:54.061
Happy Halloween. guys.

393
00:30:54.144 --> 00:30:55.563
