a century ago.</i>

402
00:31:23.382 --> 00:31:26.510
<i>seven people. including my
brother. have been murdered.</i>

403
00:31:38.898 --> 00:31:41.191
<i>I'm Frederick Loren.</i>

404
00:31:41.317 --> 00:31:43.527
