516
00:38:19.715 --> 00:38:22.050
Maybe I'm just dreaming.

517
00:38:23.552 --> 00:38:25.721
I never really
believed in ghosts.

518
00:38:26.930 --> 00:38:29.224
[Bell dings]

519
00:38:35.939 --> 00:38:37.858
I was in a lock-in once.

520
00:38:41.320 --> 00:38:42.320
What?

521
00:38:42.946 --> 00:38:45.115
I was with this
